description:
&lt;h1&gt;Estates Maintenance Worker - Band 3&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The Royal United Hospitals Bath (RUH) NHS Foundation Trust are looking to recruit an Estates Maintenance Worker (EMW), as part of the Operational Team within Estates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting directly to the Estates Officers Operations, you will be working alongside the Operational Team to deliver a comprehensive and quality service across site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work operationally to support the Maintenance Team with routine tasks and minor works, as well as liaising and interacting with other staff members within the Estates Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity for those wishing to join the NHS within Estates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team you will be joining are the most recent winners of the RUH’s trust wide ‘Team of the Year’, with exceptional staff survey scores and a positive culture based on continuous improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal enquiries regarding the post are welcome and should be addressed to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nicky Bonner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Estates Officer (Operations)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email: nicky.bonner@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Office: 01225 826926&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
